How the Link Works

All Imps reference the same link_token.

They do NOT share full mutable state.
They share:
	•	base context
	•	compressed updates
	•	evaluation signals

⸻

Update Protocol

Each Imp writes:

Δ_i = {
  new insight,
  score update,
  contradictions,
  confidence shift
}

To:

link_token.update_log.append(Δ_i)


⸻

Convergence Function

Global_State = Aggregate(Δ_1 ... Δ_n)

Where aggregation:
	•	reinforces consistent signals
	•	dampens noise
	•	flags contradictions

⸻

Translation:

The “hive mind” is not constant syncing—
it’s periodic compression and reconciliation

